A teak wall decoration can be built in the Decoration space of the Dining Room, Combat Room, and Throne Room in a player-owned house. It requires 36 Construction to build, and when built it gives 180 experience. The player must have a hammer and a saw in their inventory to build it.

A '''teak wall decoration''' can be built in the [[Decoration space]] of the [[Dining Room]], [[Combat Room]], and [[Throne Room]] in a [[player-owned house]]. It requires 36 [[Construction]] to build, and when built it gives 180 [[experience]]. The player must have a [[hammer]] and a [[saw]] in their inventory to build it.
